					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If Y=224 ($E0) blanks the screen, then you probably have the cartridge set to 256x480 (aka vertical arrangement or horizontal mirroring), and it's reading the wrong nametable. Try setting bit 1 of the value you write to $2000, that is, ORing it with the value $02.<br /><br /><br />EDIT: corrected brain fart</div>

